\/g><\/svg><\/span> <span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-label wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-recipe-servings-label\">Makes <\/span><span class=\"wprm-recipe-servings wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-servings-2126 wprm-recipe-servings-adjustable-tooltip wprm-block-text-uppercase\" data-initial-servings=\"\" data-recipe=\"2126\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\">4<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wprm-recipe-meta-container wprm-recipe-times-container wprm-recipe-details-container wprm-recipe-details-container-separate wprm-block-text-uppercase\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-block-container wprm-recipe-block-container-separate wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-recipe-time-container wprm-recipe-prep-time-container\" style=\"\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-label wprm-block-text-bold wprm-recipe-time-label wprm-recipe-prep-time-label\">Prep Time <\/span><span class=\"wprm-recipe-time wprm-block-text-uppercase\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-prep_time wprm-recipe-prep_time-minutes\">15<span class=\"sr-only screen-reader-text wprm-screen-reader-text\"> minutes<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-unit wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-prep_time-unit wprm-recipe-prep_timeunit-minutes\" aria-hidden=\"true\">mins<\/span><\/span><\/div><div class=\"wprm-recipe-block-container wprm-recipe-block-container-separate wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-recipe-time-container wprm-recipe-cook-time-container\" style=\"\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-label wprm-block-text-bold wprm-recipe-time-label wprm-recipe-cook-time-label\">Cook Time <\/span><span class=\"wprm-recipe-time wprm-block-text-uppercase\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-cook_time wprm-recipe-cook_time-minutes\">10<span class=\"sr-only screen-reader-text wprm-screen-reader-text\"> minutes<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"wprm-recipe-details-unit wprm-recipe-details-minutes wprm-recipe-cook_time-unit wprm-recipe-cook_timeunit-minutes\" aria-hidden=\"true\">mins<\/span><\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wprm-spacer\" style=\"height: 30px;\"><\/div>\n<div id=\"recipe-2126-ingredients\" class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredients-container wprm-recipe-ingredients-no-images wprm-recipe-2126-ingredients-container wprm-block-text-normal wprm-ingredient-style-regular wprm-recipe-images-before\" data-recipe=\"2126\" data-servings=\"4\"><h3 class=\"wprm-recipe-header wprm-recipe-ingredients-header wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-align-left wprm-header-decoration-none\" style=\"\">Ingredients<\/h3><div class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-group\"><ul class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredients\"><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"1\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">1<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\"><a href=\"https:\/\/toscanoauthentic.com.au\/product\/traditional-waffles-copy-copy\/\" class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-link\">pack <u><strong>Toscano Frozen Homestyle Cinnamon &amp; Apple Flavoured Waffles<\/strong><\/u><\/a><\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes-faded\">(8 waffles)<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"2\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">2<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-unit\">L<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">tub vanilla ice cream<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"3\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-amount\">300<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-unit\">g<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">dark chocolate,<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes-faded\">chopped<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" data-uid=\"4\"><span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-name\">chopped pistachios,<\/span>&#32;<span class=\"wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes wprm-recipe-ingredient-notes-faded\">to sprinkle<\/span><\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"wprm-layout-column wprm-column-width-50\">\n\n\t\t\n\n<div id=\"recipe-2126-instructions\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instructions-container wprm-recipe-2126-instructions-container wprm-block-text-normal\" data-recipe=\"2126\"><h3 class=\"wprm-recipe-header wprm-recipe-instructions-header wprm-block-text-uppercase wprm-align-left wprm-header-decoration-none\" style=\"\">Instructions<\/h3><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-group\"><ul class=\"wprm-recipe-instructions\"><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2126-step-0-0\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"display: block;\">To warm your <a href=\"https:\/\/toscanoauthentic.com.au\/product\/traditional-waffles-copy-copy\/\"><u><strong>Toscano Homestyle Cinnamon &amp; Apple Waffles<\/strong><\/u><\/a>, either<\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\">a) preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C (200\u00b0C fan-forced). Place waffles on a baking tray. Bake for 3-4 minutes or until heated through. <\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\">b) place in a toaster on lowest setting and toast for 1-2 minutes or until heated through. <\/span><div class=\"wprm-spacer\"><\/div><span style=\"display: block;\">c)\u00a0preheat your air fryer to 160\u00b0C and heat waffles for 2 minutes or until heated through.<\/span><\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2126-step-0-1\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Remove and cool on a wire rack.<\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2126-step-0-2\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"display: block;\">Working quickly, remove the ice cream from the tub in one large piece. Using a long knife cut the ice cream horizontally into 4cm-thick slices. Use a large cookie cutter, slightly smaller than the diameter of the waffles, to cut 4 ice cream discs. Sandwich each disk between cooled waffles. Place on a tray lined with baking paper and place in the freezer to firm up. Save the ice cream offcuts for another use. Alternatively, scoop large balls of ice cream and sandwich firmly between a pair of waffles. Press down gently until the ice cream is evenly distributed between the waffles.<\/span><\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2126-step-0-3\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Put the chocolate in a microwave safe bowl and microwave on medium in 30 second bursts until 80% melted, stirring in between bursts. Stir until chocolate is completely melted and smooth.<\/div><\/li><li id=\"wprm-recipe-2126-step-0-4\" class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><div class=\"wprm-recipe-instruction-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Dip the ice cream sandwiches in the chocolate and sprinkle with nuts. Return to the freezer to set before enjoying.<\/div><\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2233,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"wprm-recipe-roundup-name":"","wprm-recipe-roundup-description":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[106,174],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-2158","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-all-recipes","8":"category-sweet"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/y